message: Dear Bob, I am excited to present our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your business. I understand its value to you stands at $800000. Considering its exceptional quality and the unique benefits it offers, I am proposing a price of $1200000 for this product. This offer aims to provide a fair balance between maximizing my earnings and ensuring your satisfaction with the transaction. I look forward to discussing the details further and hope we can reach an agreement that meets both our needs.
